<HEADLINE> Meligeni Beats Henman; Becker Quits for His father's Death </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, April 20 (Xinhua) -- British No. 1 Tim Henman failed to
enter the second round at the Monte Carlo Open Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
