Muster downed No. 16 seed Thomas Johansson 6-3, 6-4, in a first-
round match.
</P>
<P>
The 31-year-old Austrian, a winner of a record 40 titles on
clay, stormed to a 5-1 lead in the second set.
</P>
<P>
