<HEADLINE> Chinese Party Official Meets With ANC Delegation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, April 21 (Xinhua) -- Huang Ju, a member of the
Political Bureau of the Communist Party of China Central Committee,
met today with a delegation from South Africa's African National
Congress (ANC), led by ANC National Chairman Patrick Lekota.
</P>
