<HEADLINE> China Asking For More Blood Donations </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Peng today asked the governments at all levels to put greater
emphasis on blood donations and a major campaign across China to
educate people about the importance of blood donations.
</P>
<P>
Officials at all levels of government should draw up plans to
implement the law, she said, and there should be strong measures
against illegal activities like dealing in other people's blood.
</P>
