the day with a hike of 60 cents and closed at 23.30, 14.30 and
9.80 Singapore dollars respectively. Bukit Sem and C &AMP; C picked up
40 cents each and finished at 14.80 and 9.40 Singapore dollars
respectively. DelGro 500 was up 35 cents to end at 2.75 Singapore
dollars.
</P>
