Australian dollars.
</P>
<P>
In the gold sector, the industry sub index fell 25.4 points to
1009.6 points.
</P>
<P>
The spot price of gold bullion on Wednesday afternoon in Sydney
was 284.10 U.S. dollars an ounce, compared to 284.90 U.S. dollars
on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
National turnover was 462.7 million stocks traded for 908.32
million U.S. dollars.
</P>
<P>
Falling stocks outnumbered rising stocks 503 to 390 and 293
stocks remained steady. 
