(BJP) lost a confidence motion by the narrowest margin of one vote
last Saturday in Lok Sabha, the lower house of Indian parliament.
</P>
<P>
The Congress should prove to the president that it would be
supported by at least 270 parliament members, many of them from
smaller parties, in an alternative government. 
