PARIS, April 21 (Xinhua) -- France insisted Wednesday that NATO
carry out air dropping operations over Kosovo to send food and
medicines to the displaced people there, despite high risks for
such operations.
</P>
<P>
France made the appeal at a meeting of NATO Council gathering
ambassadors of its member countries in Brussels, said French
officials.
