<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, April 21 (Xinhua) -- The troops of the anti-Taliban
alliance are reported to have captured Bamyan city, capital of the
central Afghan province of Bamyan, Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Fighting, which started early Wednesday morning, is still going
on in the districts of Daree Shekari and Shashpool in Bamyan
province, Saad Mohseni from Harrakat-e-Islami of Afghanistan, one
