are textile factories, incurred a loss of nearly 34 million
dollars in the same period.
</P>
<P>
Major efforts have been underway to ensure that members of the
administrations assigned to these enterprises are drawn from
various professional fields, said the official, adding that a
total of 596 experts including legal, management and engineering
staff are needed for the job at the moment. 
