<HEADLINE> New Zealand Stocks Close Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WELLINGTON, April 21 (Xinhua) -- The New Zealand sharemarket
closed
higher here Wednesday as the NZSE40 Index ended 6 points higher at
2,198
with a turnover of 69 million New Zealand dollars (38 million U.S.

