cents respectively, Fletcher Building added 2 to 262 cents and Air
New
Zealand-A 1 cent to 273 cents.
</P>
<P>
Ports Auckland lost 30 cents to 570 cents, Baycorp Holdings 18
to
1,002 cents, Fletcher Paper 10 to 160 cents, Fletcher Forests 4 to
84
cents and Auckland Airport 2 cents to 300 cents. 
</P>
