course.
</P>
<P>
He said Tuesday that in line with this commitment, the
government has come out with a power sector development policy,
which sets out the nature, scope and timing of the reforms, to be
implemented over three years, beginning this year, the Ghana News
Agency (GNA) reported.
</P>
<P>
 At a press briefin-Kena said it covers
policy framework, power sector reform and setting of priorities
over the three-year period.
