<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 21 (Xinhua) -- The Pinghu oil and gas field, the
first of its kind in the East China Sea, began operation today and
will provide 400,000 cubic meters of gas to nearby Shanghai daily
in its initial stage.
</P>
