<HEADLINE> Four Finalists Announced for NBA Sportsmanship Award </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, April 20 (xinhua) -- Eric Snow of the Philadelphia
76ers, Hersey Hawkins of Seattle, Kevin Garnett of Minnesota and
Vince Carter of Toronto were the finalists chosen by a five-member
panel of former players as divisional winners for the NBA
Sportsmanship Award.
</P>
