last two have gone to point guards Terrell Brandon of Cleveland
and Avery Johnson of San Antonio.
</P>
<P>
The award is voted on by 118 media members who regularly cover
the NBA. Former NBA players Alex English, Doc Rivers, Kenny Smith,
Isiah Thomas and Satch Sanders chose the divisional winners from a
pool of 29 team nominees. 
