<HEADLINE> Chinese Air Force Establishes Oil Supply System </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 21 (Xinhua) -- The Chinese Air Force has
established a modern system which supplies domestically-produced
oil for all aircraft and ground-to-air weapons.
</P>
<P>
